sport
Homonym Number: 1
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:3
Definition:as a term of address, often with slightly derogatory overtones, or suggestion of aggression towards or dislike of the person addressed (cf SORT) [AND as a familiar form of address chiefly Aust 1923]
